AWS S3 Static Website Hosting Project

Project Overview
This project demonstrates how to **host a static website using Amazon S3** â€” one of the most cost-effective and beginner-friendly
methods for deploying a website in the AWS Cloud.

The goal was to build a **simple, publicly accessible website** stored in an S3 bucket, apply the correct **permissions, bucket policies, and versioning**, and implement 
a **lifecycle configuration** for cost optimization.
